  "description": "<p>随着存储技术发展的越来越成熟，<strong>IBM决定将企业级一级存储方案全部采用闪存存储介质，期望可以获得更快的传输速度。</strong>为此，IBM欲投入100万美元将闪存集成到服务器和存储系统中去，并对外推出旗下仅采用这类固态存储方案的设备。</p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2e32e9e1/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243520.htm&amp;t=IBM%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%85%A8%E7%BA%BF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%97%AA%E5%AD%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243520.htm&amp;t=IBM%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%85%A8%E7%BA%BF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%97%AA%E5%AD%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243520.htm&amp;t=IBM%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%85%A8%E7%BA%BF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%97%AA%E5%AD%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F243520.htm&amp;t=IBM%E5%B0%86%E4%B8%BA%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%9A%E4%B8%80%E7%BA%A7%E5%AD%98%E5%82%A8%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E5%85%A8%E7%BA%BF%E5%B8%83%E5%B1%80%E9%97%AA%E5%AD%98%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share